section.def:
dangerous part (危險部分), in
                                    relation to any plant, means a part specified in Schedule
                                                1;

further assessment (進一步評估) means an assessment made in accordance with section 25(1),
            and includes such an assessment as varied after review in accordance with section
                25(3);

manual handling operation (體力處理操作), in relation to a load, means moving or
            supporting the load (including lifting, lowering, pushing, pulling and carrying the
            load) by a person’s hands or arms or by some other form of bodily effort;

preliminary assessment (初步評估) means an assessment made in accordance with section 23(1)
            or (2), and includes such an assessment as varied after review in accordance with
                section 23(4);
